title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - Moe Pope
description:
Meet Moe Pope and the members of Quills who each grew up in different places but now all reside in Boston, MA. Listen to the band discuss what music has influenced them individually, how they came together as a band and their last experience in the recording studio.
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks visit:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
